melting.configuration

Enum RegisterMethods.MethodType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RegisterMethods.MethodType>
      • melting.configuration.RegisterMethods.MethodType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RegisterMethods.MethodType>
    Enclosing class:
    RegisterMethods

    public static enum RegisterMethods.MethodType
extends java.lang.Enum<RegisterMethods.MethodType>
    Represents a particular type of method (e.g., approximative method, double dangling end method, Mg/Na mix correction method). This enum provides a (Java) method to get a list of all the (thermodynamic) methods of that type.
